	(13, 'com_content.article.3', '', '2024-06-18 09:43:15', 360, 5645, 'dbd0b3a843fdb83b1f8b8b7ae68478ea1adfc79f', '{"id":"3","asset_id":146,"title":" TTQLKTX k\\u00fd k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi Ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng BIDV \\u2013 Chi nh\\u00e1nh \\u0110\\u00f4ng S\\u00e0i G\\u00f2n","alias":"ttqlktx-ky-k-t-h-p-tac-toan-di-n-v-i-ngan-hang-bidv-chi-nhanh-dong-sai-gon","introtext":"<div class=\\"description\\">\\r\\n<p>Ng\\u00e0y 03\\/01\\/2024, t\\u1ea1i h\\u1ed9i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng F1, K\\u00fd t\\u00fac x\\u00e1 x\\u00e1 khu B, Trung t\\u00e2m Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd K\\u00fd t\\u00fac x\\u00e1 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c l\\u1ec5 k\\u00fd k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi Ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng BIDV \\u2013 Chi nh\\u00e1nh \\u0110\\u00f4ng S\\u00e0i G\\u00f2n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"content\\">\\r\\n<p><input alt=\\"\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/ktx.vnuhcm.edu.vn\\/public\\/userfiles\\/news\\/kyket%20(1).jpg\\" type=\\"image\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tham d\\u1ef1 l\\u1ec5 k\\u00fd k\\u1ebft c\\u00f3 \\u00d4ng\\u00a0<span lang=\\"EN-GB\\">L\\u00ea Trung Th\\u00e0nh - Ph\\u00f3 T\\u1ed5ng Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c Ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng BIDV; \\u00d4ng \\u0110\\u1eb7ng V\\u0103n Ki\\u00ean - Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c BIDV Chi nh\\u00e1nh \\u0110\\u00f4ng S\\u00e0i G\\u00f2n; \\u00d4ng Nguy\\u1ec5n Cao Minh - Ph\\u00f3 Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c Ban Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p Ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng BIDV;\\u00a0ThS. Tr\\u1ea7n Anh C\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u2013 Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch C\\u00f4ng \\u0111o\\u00e0n, Ph\\u00f3 Tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng Ban, Ban C\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0110HQG-HCM;\\u00a0ThS. T\\u0103ng H\\u1eefu Th\\u1ee7y \\u2013 Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c TTQLKTX; \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n l\\u00e3nh \\u0111\\u1ea1o Ban k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch \\u2013 \\u0110\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban C\\u00e1n s\\u1ef1 \\u0110o\\u00e0n \\u0110HQG-HCM; Ban Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c, l\\u00e3nh \\u0111\\u1ea1o ch\\u1ee7 ch\\u1ed1t Ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng BIDV \\u2013 Chi nh\\u00e1nh \\u0110\\u00f4ng S\\u00e0i G\\u00f2n; Ban Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c, l\\u00e3nh \\u0111\\u1ea1o c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 vi\\u00ean ch\\u1ee9c, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi lao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c t\\u1ea1i TTQLKTX.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><input alt=\\"\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/ktx.vnuhcm.edu.vn\\/public\\/userfiles\\/news\\/8b82e102-f82f-43de-a590-5e5cdb14cf5c.jpg\\" type=\\"image\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-GB\\">Theo th\\u1ecfa thu\\u1eadn, trong th\\u1eddi h\\u1ea1n 5 n\\u0103m, hai \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb s\\u1ebd h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n trong c\\u00e1c l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u1ea5p c\\u00e1c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 thanh to\\u00e1n, d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ti\\u1ec1n m\\u1eb7t trong thanh to\\u00e1n t\\u1ea1i Trung t\\u00e2m Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd K\\u00fd t\\u00fac x\\u00e1. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng BIDV \\u2013 Chi nh\\u00e1nh \\u0110\\u00f4ng S\\u00e0i G\\u00f2n s\\u1ebd t\\u00e0i tr\\u1ee3 kinh ph\\u00ed 3 t\\u1ef7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 tri\\u1ec3n<\\/span><span lang=\\"EN-GB\\">\\u00a0khai d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n v\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t an ninh, an to\\u00e0n c\\u00e1c t\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 t\\u1ea1i K\\u00fd t\\u00fac x\\u00e1.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><input alt=\\"\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/ktx.vnuhcm.edu.vn\\/public\\/userfiles\\/news\\/trongcaynganhang.jpg\\" type=\\"image\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span lang=\\"EN-GB\\">Sau l\\u1ec5 k\\u00fd k\\u1ebft, c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ea1i bi\\u1ec3u\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u0111\\u00e3 tham gia tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e2y \\u201cV\\u00ec m\\u1ed9t K\\u00fd t\\u00fac x\\u00e1 xanh\\u201d v\\u00e0 tham quan tri\\u1ec3n l\\u00e3m \\u201cBi\\u1ec3n \\u2013 \\u0110\\u1ea3o Vi\\u1ec7t Nam: Nh\\u1eefng minh ch\\u1ee9ng l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed\\u201d v\\u00e0 tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ea1i \\u1ea3o 3 chi\\u1ec1u \\u201cKh\\u00f4ng gian v\\u0103n h\\u00f3a H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh\\u201d t\\u1ea1i Kh\\u00f4ng gian tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb \\u0110HQG-HCM \\u2013 Qu\\u1ea3ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ed9t m\\u1ed1c ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n Qu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa \\u2013 K\\u00fd t\\u00fac x\\u00e1 khu B.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>","fulltext":"","state":"1","catid":9,"created":"2024-06-18 09:09:00","created_by":"360","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2024-06-18 09:43:15","modified_by":360,"checked_out":360,"checked_out_time":"2024-06-18 09:42:50","publish_up":"2024-06-18 09:09:00","publish_down":null,"images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/news\\\\\\/portfolio-img-2.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/news\\\\\\/portfolio-img-2.jpg?width=500&height=314\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"images\\\\\\/news\\\\\\/portfolio-img-2.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/news\\\\\\/portfolio-img-2.jpg?width=500&height=314\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":\\"\\",\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":\\"\\",\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmo